  },
  {
    "id": "page_0286-b003",
    "page_key": 286,
    "order": 3,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "In other words, we optimize over a new set of variables $\\lbrace f\\_{i}\\rbrace$ where adjacent values cannot change by more than one.",
